    public class MacUIHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.simplericity.macify.eawt.ApplicationListener
    Class that adds elements to agree with Apple's Human Interface Guidelines (HIG) such as a dock icon and menu bar on OSX. Uses Simplericity's Macify library for platform independence.
